    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/retail-management/RMG/917.html" title="RMG 917 - Experiential Learning - International Study" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">RMG 917</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Experiential Learning - International Study</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">This course examines consumption patterns, retail formats and operations, as well as sourcing opportunities and challenges in a defined region. Students will participate in a 10 day international learning experience in a chosen country. The course will be taught by Ryerson retail faculty but local industry experts will be invited to address various topics.</div>
	
	
