		<div class="courseListDescription">Given the dynamic nature of the retail industry, leaders are required to develop productive and engaging organizations which are also primed for disruption and innovation. In this course, students develop customer focused organizational leadership strategies focused on innovative problem solving processes and organizational alignment. They also develop personal leadership skills oriented to the development of an engaged, productive workforce.</div>
	
	
